metadata.name: Sample Pack One
metadata.description:
Lausten Found's first web3 drum sample pack, exclusively available through our NFT release. This pack is loaded with high-quality, recorded and sampled drum sounds that will take your beats to the next level.

Featuring a wide range of styles, from classic boom bap to modern trap, this sample pack has everything you need to create the perfect foundation for your tracks. Each sample has been crafted and meticulously processed to deliver maximum punch and clarity.

Whether you're a seasoned producer or just starting out, this sample pack is an essential tool for any hip hop producer. Unlock your copy now and get instant access to over 100 top-quality drum sounds that will elevate your beats to new heights. Don't miss out on this must-have genesis pack!

Be sure to redeem via: Three Dots > View Website  
or using:  
https://laustenfound.com/products/lausten-found-sample-pack-1
